U.K. Treasury Sets Deadline for Submitting Tote Bids, Times Says

-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 
2011-05-29T10:03:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/u-k-treasury-sets-deadline-for-submitting-tote-bids-times-says.html
The U.K. Treasury has set a June 2
deadline for final bids for the Tote bookmaking business, the
 Sunday Times  reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Sports Investment Partners and Betfred Ltd. are both
bidding for the U.K. government-owned business, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
